<h2><a name="size" id="size">size</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;valarray&gt;</span>
    size_t size<span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span>;</pre>
<p>
The size() function returns the number of elements in the valarray.
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">   <span class="co2">#include &lt;valarray&gt;</span>
   <span class="co2">#include &lt;iostream&gt;</span>
&nbsp;
   <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> vd<span class="br0">&#91;</span><span class="br0">&#93;</span> <span class="sy0">=</span> <span class="br0">&#123;</span><span class="nu0">1</span><span class="sy0">,</span><span class="nu0">2</span><span class="sy0">,</span><span class="nu0">3</span><span class="sy0">,</span><span class="nu0">4</span><span class="sy0">,</span><span class="nu0">5</span><span class="br0">&#125;</span>;
   std<span class="sy0">::</span><span class="me2">valarray</span><span class="sy0">&lt;</span>int<span class="sy0">&gt;</span> v1<span class="br0">&#40;</span>vd<span class="sy0">,</span><span class="nu0">5</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span>;
   std<span class="sy0">::</span><a href="http://www.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/009695399/functions/cout.html"><span class="kw3">cout</span></a> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> v1.<span class="me1">size</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span><span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="sy0">&lt;&lt;</span> std<span class="sy0">::</span><span class="me2">endl</span>;</pre>
<p>
Will produce this output:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">   <span class="nu0">5</span></pre>
